#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rkward; is meant to be(come) an easy to use graphical frontend to the "
"powerful &R; language for statistical computing. Since &R; is a full "
"featured programming language, &rkward; will never be able to offer a "
"complete GUI for everything in &R;. However, &rkward; strives to make common "
"task simple, to provide an easy entry point for newcomers, while at the same "
"time, transparent access to the full power of the underlying &R; language is "
"provided for advanced users."
msgstr ""
"&rkward; naj bi bil (postal) grafični vmesnik, ki je enostaven za uporabo k "
"zmogljivemu programu &R; jeziku za statistično računalništvo. Ker &R; je "
"programski jezik z vsemi funkcijami, &rkward; nikoli ne bo mogel ponuditi "
"popolnega GUI za vse v &R;. Vendar &rkward; si prizadeva narediti običajno "
"nalogo preprosto, zagotoviti enostavno vstopno točko za novince, hkrati pa "
"pregleden dostop do celotne moči osnovnega &R; jezik je na voljo za napredne "
"uporabnike."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &rkward;"
msgstr "Uporaba &rkward;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most documentation is available from inside &rkward; itself by selecting "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Help</guimenu><guimenuitem>Help</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in &rkward; from the menu, <emphasis>not</emphasis> in this "
"document."
msgstr ""
"Večina dokumentacije je na voljo znotraj &rkward; tako, da izberete "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pomoč</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pomoč</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> v &rkward; v meniju, <emphasis>ne</emphasis> v tem dokumentu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A useful guide to getting started with &rkward; is <ulink url=\"https://"
"rkward.kde.org/User_Documentation\">User Documentation Section in the "
"&rkward; wiki</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Koristen vodnik za začetek uporabe &rkward; je <ulink url=\"https://rkward."
"kde.org/User_Documentation\">oddelek z uporabniško dokumentacijo v &rkward; "
"wiki</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please go there for an introduction to &rkward;, and contact us, if you can "
"help with creating user documentation."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite tja za uvod v &rkward; in nas kontaktirajte, če lahko pomagate pri "
"ustvarjanju uporabniške dokumentacije."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "Developer's Guide to &rkward;"
msgstr "Vodnik za razvijalce za &rkward;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&rkward; can be extended without the need to recompile using plugins. "
"Extensive documentation on this should be included with &rkward; in DocBook "
"format, and is available in &HTML; format <ulink url=\"https://api.kde.org/"
"doc/rkwardplugins\">here</ulink>. (TODO: figure out, how to include this in "
"the documentation)."
msgstr ""
"&rkward; se lahko razširi brez potrebe po ponovnem prevajanju z uporabo "
"vtičnikov. Obsežna dokumentacija o tem mora biti vključena v &rkward; v "
"formatu DocBook in je na voljo v &HTML; formatu <ulink url=\"https://api.kde."
"org/doc/rkwardplugins\">tukaj</ulink>. (ZA NAREDITI: ugotovite, kako to "
"vključiti v dokumentacijo)."

